high_descs: Take a step to your right then walk to the sink.
Open the cabinet under the left side of the left sink and grab the bottle of liquid soap under there then close the door.
Take a small step backwards then a step to your left.
Put the soap on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put liquid soap on the toilet.

high_descs: Head toward the sink across the room.
Open the left-side cabinet under the sink and take out the bottle of soap.
Turn to the left and head toward the toilet on the right.
Put the bottle of soap on top of the toilet next to the spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a bottle of soap on top of a toilet.

high_descs: pick up the pump bottle from the counter
take the bottle to the toilet
put the bottle on the back of the toilet
anns.task_desc: take the pump bottle from the sink to the toilet
